title: Bastille - BBC Radio 1 Big Weekend 2018 [Video Album]
description:
The BBC is the National Public Service broadcaster of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland and this Biggest Weekend concert was held in place of Glastonbury who are taking a year out.

It is nation wide with 4 venues,  Perth in Scotland, The Titanic Shipyard, Belfast Northern Ireland, Swansea Wales and Coventry in England were the locations and they were Broadcast live across the BBC on TV, Radio and Digital streaming with catch up TV showing every second of every event at later dates so the viewer missed nothing.

175,000 low cost tickets were all that we offered for this one off historic music event, which featured North American bands and singers too.  Much more to come over the next day or two.
